data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom gem, nestled within a peaceful neighborhood. This elegant two-story home boasts a thoughtful open floor plan, combining modern design with comfort and functionality. Step inside and be captivated by the seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. The heart of the home, the kitchen, features luxurious granite countertops that perfectly complement the sleek cabinetry. A grand and inviting island takes center stage, providing ample space for culinary creations and delightful conversations. Ascending the staircase, you'll discover a haven of relaxation in the upstairs main bedroom. Unwind in the generously sized room, complete with a walk-in closet that effortlessly accommodates your wardrobe needs. The main bathroom offers double sinks and a stand up shower with private washroom. A private and versatile flex space on the upper level presents endless possibilities - a home office, a cozy reading nook, or even a fitness retreat, tailored to your desires.With a total of 5 bedrooms, there's ample room for family and guests, while the 3 well-appointed bathrooms ensure convenience for everyone. This home also offers an indoor laundry room for your convenience. Outdoors you'll find a pavered patio area, the perfect spot for gathering with friends and family. This community also offers a clubhouse, swimming pool and playground! Conveniently located near shopping and dining, with easy access to Hwy 27, this home offers the perfect blend of modern living and timeless appeal. Don't miss the opportunity to call this meticulously designed, 5-bedroom beauty your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the harmonious blend of comfort and sophistication that awaits within these walls.
